long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatically calculate maturity dates of securities when browsing. 

This extension is open source to provide full transparency as to what the extension does. None of your data will be collected or analyzed. You can view the source code for this extension here
